##### chapter X41m - nuclear power gambit

.extra-short.medium-small[Business is like nuclear reaction. If you build cirtical mass of human connections then a random idea can cause a chain reaction.

Ideas an neutrons have to be moderated to keep the process under control. Unsupervised chain reaction can cause serious disasters and long term concamination of relations.

On the other hand slow nuclear process can lead to extremly efficient social power production which can be a strong motor for any kind of business.]

